        "body": "<p><code>input.nextLine();<\/code> returns a String. You need to store the result into a variable like <code>String userResponse = input.nextLine();<\/code> then in your condition do <code>if(userResponse.equalsIgnoreCase(hello))<\/code>. Because in your code you test if your variable hello is equals to your variable hello. It can only be true. You need to store the response of the user and then test if it's equal to your variable hello<\/p>\n",
